### POST: Add a player to the depth chart for NFL at Wide Receiver position
POST http://localhost:8080/api/depth-chart-data-structure/NFL/WR/add?playerId=4&playerName=New%20Player&depth=1
Content-Type: application/json

### DELETE: Remove a player from the depth chart for NFL at Wide Receiver position
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/depth-chart-data-structure/NFL/WR/remove?playerId=2
Content-Type: application/json

### GET: Retrieve the full depth chart for NFL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/depth-chart-data-structure/NFL
Content-Type: application/json

### GET: Retrieve players by position in NFL for Wide Receivers (WR)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/depth-chart-data-structure/NFL/WR
Content-Type: application/json

### GET: Retrieve players under a specific player in the WR position for NFL
# Replace `2` with the actual ID of the player you want to query under.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/depth-chart-data-structure/NFL/WR/under?playerId=2
Content-Type: application/json
